    Audit
    Annotation that enables an audit trail for the annotated method.
    AudittrailAnnotationInterceptor
    This interceptor is used to pass some audit information through to the request-object to make it available for the filters where the actual logging is triggered.
    AudittrailAnnotationInterceptorRegisterer
    This class is used to add the audittrail annotation interceptor in the interceptor registry.
